<p>
Thank you for the letter. And congratulations on your sobriety.

<p>Unfortunately, you have been misinformed. Starting at the top:
<ol>
<p><li> The line that &quot;many millions of people have gotten and stayed sober through
AA&quot; is simply untrue.
<a href="orange-effectiveness.html#Vaillant" target="_blank">A.A. is a failure
that has no better a success rate than people getting no help or program or treatment</a>.
<p>

